                <sect3>
                    <title>Vehicle Techniques</title>

                    <para>
                        There are a small number of basic vehicle skills,
                        and familiarity is required for specific vehicle
                        types. For example, <e>Pilot</e> will enable you
                        to fly any type of aircraft, though your skill roll
                        is halved if you aren't familiar with a particular
                        type.
                    </para>

                    <para>
                        Familiarity is gained by purchasing a technique, so
                        many of the vehicle techniques are for familiarity.
                        If you aren't familiar with a type of vehicle, then
                        you cannot use any techniques with that vehicle.
